Suppliers can also be blocked in local systems around the world via our IT-based Global Master Data Management process for suppliers.

Sustainability topics with a specific need for action Two focus topics play an important role in our sustainable supply chain practices, given their strong connection to other sustainability initiatives at Siemens. These include the responsible sourcing of minerals and reducing CO2e emis- sions in our supply chain.

